{
  "stem": "14292.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't know you know, or not, but the Volkswagen was not the first thing Hitler started with-- Volksradio was the first thing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He wanted the radio in every one home because he was able to influence people through his speech.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My brother, who was a Jewish student in Switzerland said that when he heard Hitler speaking, he couldn't be quiet.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He was so enthused until he read what the words he was saying.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He was just an incredible charismatic speaker.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I think that if you look at what Hitler did for the world, as far as the present is concerned, our current election is a very good example.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You have to appear in the crowd by television and other mean.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It's a salesmanship.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he was a terrific salesman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He was able to mobilize a very civilized country for his purpose and for his intent, which eventually was a very destructive one.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think we have to understand that concept, otherwise everybody think, how come this could happen?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think he was an incredible charismatic person who, from the misery of Germany, he kind of remade the Germans very proud and very prosperous.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then eventually introducing this very horrifying dogma, which he was obsessed with.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Which was number one is the hate of anything what Jews did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not was only hating about the capitalism, the bank, but he was hating the communism.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was hating even the Bible, itself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was an obsession, which eventually led to this destruction of these many, many million people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he was known.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing is the human principles was not-- they was against anything because it was an absolutely discriminatory comments, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Separating certain people as inferior.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
